    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The process of shaping glass by blowing air through a blowpipe into a glob of molten glass and forming it with tongs and shears or by rolling it against a hard surface.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
